        <updateDate>2008-05-17T16:23:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Homefront Heroes Tax Relief Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow taxpayers who do not otherwise itemize a deduction from gross income of up to $500 for amounts paid to provide care packages for members of the Armed Forces serving in a combat zone. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
